                  <head>On a walk through Gafsa</head>
               </link>
            </div>
            <div type="researchHistory">
               <p xml:space="preserve">With the exception of two texts in the Arabic dialect of Gafsan Jews (Singer 1980, 272-276) hitherto no data is published on the dialect of Gafsa, however this dialect is linguistically investigated within the TUNOCENT project.</p>
            </div>
